name: Unidentified_store_clerk
content:
A clerk of the same species as Armo Malou was the proprietor of a supply store in the town of Anchorhead on Tatooine. In 9 BBY, he served moisture farmers Owen Lars and Luke Skywalker when they found themselves in need of replacement parts for their speeder.
This Clerk runs a supply store that sells parts for vehicles and machines on Tatooine. One day, Owen and Lars and Luke Skywalker came to his store and ask Luke what he needed. Luke told him they were looking for replacement parts for their Landspeeder because Luke broke the last one. He even told him his uncle was a patient man thought Owen told him he was a patient man. Suddenly, Dardin Shull show up in the store to warn Owen that Reva was looking for him.
